      "text": "…………みなさん。楽しんで頂けましたか？\nこれから、頂点まであと三つ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ladies and gentlemen‚ did you enjoy yourselves?\nOnly three more steps until we reach the top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.56174607276918,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2571.5872605641366,
          "startTime": 65.43333333333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "私達リズノワは、ステージごとに最高スコアを\n塗り替えていくつもりですので、見ていて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With each performance‚ LizNoir strives to surpass the high score.\nWe hope you’ll watch us every step of the way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.22841273943583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 76.72841273943581
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_01/sud_vo_adv_main_01_12_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "僕はそんな約束するつもりはないけどね\nもう帰ってもいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not gonna make any promises like that.\nCan we go now?",
        "id": ""
      },
